n":"none","all_time_high":123.0,"all_time_low":67.5,"long_business_summary":"Alfa Ica (India) Limited manufactures and sells high pressure laminated sheets and compacts in India and internationally. The company offers compact grade, cubicle compact, post formable, anti-bacterial, interior and exterior grade, tough gloss, laboratory grade, fire retardant, and color compact laminates. It also provides real metal foils, dry wipe boards, tile panels, and anti-fingerprint products. The company exports its products. It serves various applications, such as furniture and door coverings, interior and wall paneling, partitions, cubicle partition and shower panels, exterior wall cladding, green chalk and white board boards, dry wipe boards, kitchen top and backsplash, anti-fingerprint laminate, tabletop, fire retardant, and other areas. Alfa Ica (India) Limited was incorporated in 1991 and is headquartered in Ahmedabad, India."}}